{"tid":226949,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【絕望求助】中國囚犯求救？ 美國女子超市買銀包內藏字條","createTime":"2017-05-02T21:08:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T23:53:57.000Z","uid":61022,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b275a976fb909b2e5112fca409ab5935554e2b51","tid":226949,"uid":61022,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T21:08:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/03/050827_b20a31a40860215e6d41c3ae7e7bec90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F03%2F050827_b20a31a40860215e6d41c3ae7e7bec90.jpg&h=299c41ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國亞利桑那州一名女子在超市買銀包，怎料發現全新的銀包內有字條，對方指自己是來自中國的囚犯，每天工作14小時，又指在中國監獄不如美國的豬狗，希望看到字條的人提供幫助。<br />\n<br />\n女子指在沃爾瑪超市（Walmart）買銀包而發現字條，對方以簡體中文書寫指自己是中國犯人，被迫加班至晚上12時，工作未能完成就挨打；他又指自己的膳食沒有油鹽，又指若犯人有病要吃藥就要扣錢，懇求看到字條的人幫助。<br />\n<br />\n女子指自己沒有方法幫助對方，但就將事件公開，希望有人提供協助。<br />\n<br />\n美國過去也有一些像K-Mart這些大量採購外包貨源的超市，被發現貨品內有類似字條。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170502&amp;guid=56637464&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170502%26guid%3D56637464%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&d=AZYGjn5ll7vy7cK20AVbo9Wu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=359c6653\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170502%26guid%3D56637464%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&h=76e0f69a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170502&amp;guid=56637464&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"c215a5d1b47e6afc62a3cae42a265db1f1d06712","tid":226949,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T22:23:16.000Z","msg":"抵啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"334ce446f7892ded03b254dd92651e2d9fee546d"